plot: Short documentary about the city of Cuzco: its history, the Sacsahuamán fortress, the archaeological museum, the temple of Coricancha, the Inca writer Garcilaso de la Vega's house, the Cathedral and the University.
title: Cuzco, ciudad dos veces imperial
